{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2032, "height": 2755, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜林元：廷行次子，武生。", "block_bbox": [179, 236, 770, 289], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜林茂：廷行三子，武生。", "block_bbox": [178, 306, 770, 359], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜林川：廷行四子，佾生。", "block_bbox": [177, 377, 769, 428], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜星五：廷用次子，生员。", "block_bbox": [177, 447, 771, 499], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜林皋：从九。", "block_bbox": [178, 518, 576, 570], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十二世杜成林：从九。", "block_bbox": [177, 590, 577, 640], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十二世杜嘉林：乙未科副榜，武陟县训导。", "block_bbox": [176, 659, 939, 712], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十二世杜泮林：从九。", "block_bbox": [177, 732, 578, 783], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十三世杜朝栋：林皋孙，佾生。", "block_bbox": [177, 802, 726, 854], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十三世杜朝楹：泮林子，配王氏，子一，公早殁，遗子希贤仅七岁，王氏守节自誓，姑李氏年老失明，王氏殷切扶持，能得其欢心，勤俭持家，严师训子，克振家声云。", "block_bbox": [173, 868, 1678, 994], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十三世杜朝梁：泮林子，从九。", "block_bbox": [177, 1012, 727, 1064], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十三世杜希贤：朝楹子，公幼失怙，克振家声，侍母至孝，人无间言。", "block_bbox": [177, 1081, 1382, 1135], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十三世杜芳春：公生于一八六八年(同治八年)，卒于一九五八年，享寿九十，一生克勤克俭，维孝维慈。八十八岁时耳不聋眼不花，身直体壮，白发长须。因劳跌伤，卧床二年而殁。卒之日，一弟、四子、十孙、十曾孙、一元孙、四儿媳、九孙女、八孙媳、二曾孙媳、五曾孙女、一元孙女，五世同堂，人称贤翁焉。\n", "block_bbox": [176, 1152, 1682, 1416], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十四世杜象贤：朝梁子，佾生。", "block_bbox": [181, 1430, 731, 1482], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十四世杜鼎新：芳春子，开封师院毕业。", "block_bbox": [180, 1499, 900, 1551], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十四世杜裔云：希贤子，公自幼勤学，通文精医，擅长针灸，技艺精湛，医德淳厚，闻名当时。渑池人民医院中医师。\n", "block_bbox": [176, 1569, 1681, 1688], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十四世杜玉琢：公乃驰名兽医，技术精湛，医德高尚，年近九旬，依然为民服务。", "block_bbox": [178, 1707, 1595, 1760], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜俊杰妻张氏：三十二岁守节，孝敬公姑，抚养孤子松范，含辛茹苦，履境难堪，积七旬时四世同堂，名闻乡里焉。\n", "block_bbox": [175, 1777, 1683, 1896], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜俊英：洛阳铭德中学毕业，执教两载，升校长。以目疾弃教从医，拜名医周学儒为师，1958年，父母辞世，乃悲伤过度，双目失明。公系当时名医，驰名邻县，德高望重，仗义疏财，求医者、请教者、议事者络绎不绝。年届七旬，乃全力组织纂修宗谱，，并口述序言。见本谱杜俊英墓碑文。\n", "block_bbox": [174, 1914, 1685, 2174], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜俊良：公自幼好学，长于史、地，编有《历史门径》，又整理有《医学汇编》。", "block_bbox": [176, 2193, 1635, 2245], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜忠琪：参加中国人民志愿军，抗美援朝，在朝鲜牺牲，安葬在朝鲜第二烈士陵园。\n", "block_bbox": [173, 2260, 1682, 2381], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜福礼：经商致富，不忘其本。详修祠读谱功德碑。\n十六世杜青松：毕业于西安地质学院，任新疆自治区地质探测队高级工程师。", "block_bbox": [174, 2399, 1575, 2523], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1793, 722, 1873, 1442], "block_id": 22, "block_order": 23}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8215706944465637, "coordinate": [174.04888916015625, 1914.95361328125, 1685.22900390625, 2174.611328125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.734058678150177, "coordinate": [176.40399169921875, 1569.059326171875, 1681.001708984375, 1688.140869140625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7112525105476379, "coordinate": [175.62896728515625, 1777.3157958984375, 1683.767822265625, 1896.6258544921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7077592611312866, "coordinate": [176.15045166015625, 1152.90087890625, 1682.396484375, 1416.41943359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6309428811073303, "coordinate": [178.55712890625, 1707.06103515625, 1595.784423828125, 1760.3203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6276630759239197, "coordinate": [173.21575927734375, 2260.643310546875, 1682.36083984375, 2381.331298828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6139339208602905, "coordinate": [180.71240234375, 1499.2357177734375, 900.1173095703125, 1551.8724365234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6083291172981262, "coordinate": [173.8851318359375, 868.8711547851562, 1678.3709716796875, 994.0993041992188]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5816816091537476, "coordinate": [181.34051513671875, 1430.918212890625, 731.4060668945312, 1482.986083984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5779874920845032, "coordinate": [177.79827880859375, 2468.4677734375, 1572.442626953125, 2521.45703125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5635466575622559, "coordinate": [177.3543701171875, 2399.860107421875, 1236.6285400390625, 2451.252197265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5525326132774353, "coordinate": [177.44586181640625, 1081.9029541015625, 1382.9609375, 1135.6368408203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5242524147033691, "coordinate": [176.95614624023438, 659.308837890625, 9